EN: Only with the power of unity can we stand up and change society.

ZH: 我们要立起身来维护正义，为弱者发声。
EN: We must stand up and uphold justice, speaking out for the weak.

ZH: 他的成功经历激励着我们立起身探索自己的潜力。
EN: His success story inspires us to stand up and explore our own potential.

ZH: 面对挑战，我们要立起身来迎接，勇往直前。
EN: In the face of challenges, we must stand up and face them bravely, moving forward.
